data.description: Looking for a retreat in the heart of Fort Walton. This home has has been freshly painted with new light fixtures, new LVP flooring, countertop and more... It also has washer and dryer hook up in the unit with washer and dryer. Enjoy kayaking or fishing of the community dock at Cinco Bayou or spend time hanging out by the pool overlooking the water. This community also offers grilling in the courtyard. All measurements are approximate and should be verified by buyer. The complex doesn't allow short term rentals or private boat slips
